author: Ryan Reynolds
description:
Captain Tom Slingsby and the @BondsFlyingRoos embody courage, determination, and teamwork. Words that hit harder in #HughJackman's thick Aussie brogue. Now go win that fourth Grand Final in Abu Dhabi, Roos. LFG.

All aboard! @BondsOz, @mondaydotcom, @BlueberryMarketsForex, and @SailGP!
title: Hugh Jackman and Ryan Reynolds Go Sailing with BONDS Flying Roos
